cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.SI

The paper deals with image denoising and imaging inverse problems, which are typically studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and information theory (cs.IT) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a new algorithm and proves its convergence, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and signal processing (cs.SI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper applies the proposed framework to data fusion in imaging, which is a topic studied in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
